        },
        {
            "title": "貝森特宣布美國財政部干預了阿根廷外匯市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>周四在社交媒體發文宣布，美國與阿根廷央行敲定了一項200億美元的貨幣互換框架。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特還表示，美國周四直接購買了阿根廷披索以支持阿根廷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特稱：「美國財政部已做好準備，立即採取一切必要的非常措施以穩定市場。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Says $20 Billion US-Argentina Currency Swap Finalized</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E4%BA%86%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-191222344.html",
